wdi2-NE.RSB.GNFS.KN.def: External balance on goods and services (formerly resource balance) equals exports of goods and services minus imports of goods and services (previously nonfactor services). Data are in constant local currency.
wdi2-NE.RSB.GNFS.KN.name: External balance on goods and services
wdi2-NE.RSB.GNFS.KN.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
